commit_message:
Sync models with migrations

Remove a difference between models and migrations in different dialects:
- add missing foreign key to pci_devices;
- add indexes for postgres declared only for mysql;
- add foreign key to bm_interfaces;
- rename unique constraints for which name was skipped in declaration.

bp: db-sync-models-with-migrations

Change-Id: I678c01e91dd25f1f0add38dd43e7248d56498257

